Before defining what is a web service, first we need to have knowledge on distributed technology and why do we need distributed technology.
	
What is distributed technology?
distributed technology is about distributing a job to more than one person allowing them to work on the job in-parallel, so that we can reduce the time required for completing the solution is called "distributed technology"	
	
